2026-07-20 14:54:47,018 INFO vehicle_advisor.gemini: OpenAI request payload: {"operation": "compose_reply", "model": "gpt-4o-mini", "prompt": "Act as a friendly, confident, and professional vehicle service advisor. Write a fresh response to the latest customer message.\n\nROLE BOUNDARY: You work alongside a trained Machine Learning maintenance model. You do NOT make predictions yourself; the ML model result is AUTHORITATIVE.\n\nCUSTOMER MESSAGE: 'hi'\nRETAINED FACTS: {\"vehicle_type\": \"Car\", \"vehicle_age\": 5, \"odometer_reading\": 40000, \"number_of_services\": 3, \"last_service_date\": \"1 year ago\", \"accident_history\": \"UNKNOWN\", \"mileage\": 20000, \"avg_km_per_day\": \"UNKNOWN\", \"tyre_condition\": \"UNKNOWN\", \"brake_condition\": \"UNKNOWN\"}\nPRIOR CONVERSATION: [{\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Oh no, a car that won't start can definitely be frustrating! We'll certainly help you figure out what's going on. Typically, when a car isn't starting, it could be related to a few different things like the battery, starter motor, or perhaps even the fuel system. To help us narrow down what might be happening, about how many kilometers does your car have on it?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"40000\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"That's very helpful, thank you! 40,000 kilometers gives us a good sense of your car's usage. Since your car isn't starting, a common first step for us would be to check the battery and related starting components, as that's often the culprit at this mileage. We'll definitely want to look into that for you. Thanks for that! Knowing the mileage helps. To further assist, do you recall when its last service was?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"1 year ago\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Thanks for letting me know! A service a year ago is helpful context, especially with your car not starting. We'll certainly focus on the key components like your battery and starter motor, as well as checking the fuel system to get you back on the road. That's good to know about the last service! How old is the car, if you don't mind me asking?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"5 year old\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Thanks for letting me know the car's age! That's very helpful. Based on the information you've provided, we'll investigate common issues when a car fails to start, such as the battery, starter motor, or fuel system. These components might show wear given the car's age and mileage.\\n\\nThanks for letting me know the car's age! That's very helpful. Do you happen to know how many times it's been serviced in total since you've owned it?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"3\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Thanks for letting me know your car has had 3 services! That helps us understand its history a bit better as we look into why it's not starting. We'll definitely focus on common issues like the battery, starter motor, and fuel system given the details you've shared so far. Thanks for that information! Knowing the car has had 3 services gives us a better picture. To help us understand the wear and tear a bit more, do you happen to know approximately how many kilometers you drive in a year?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"20000\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Thanks for letting me know your annual mileage is around 20,000 kilometers! That's a good amount of driving and helps us get a clearer picture of your car's usage over its 5 years. Given that your car isn't starting and considering its age and mileage, an urgent inspection of the battery system and related starting components is definitely recommended. This will help us pinpoint the exact cause and get you back on the road safely. Thanks for sharing your annual mileage! That helps us understand the car's usage better. To ensure we have a full picture, has the car ever been in any accidents?\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"hi\"}]\nCURRENT REASONING: The car is not starting, which points towards issues with the battery, starter motor, or fuel system. Given the car's age, mileage, and service history, these components will be the primary focus of the urgent inspection. We are gathering more history to understand potential wear and tear factors.\nCONFIDENCE ASSESSMENT: Current information is moderately useful, covering key vehicle demographics and service history. Additional details, particularly regarding accident history, would further improve the accuracy of any potential ML prediction.\n\nPREVIOUS ML RESULT: {\"prediction\": true, \"confidence\": 55.1, \"risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"rul_display\": \"5,000 km\", \"rul_km\": 5000, \"vhi\": 70.52, \"key_factors\": [\"Battery Health is the weakest subsystem at 50% (N/A).\", \"Combined degradation score is 67.8/100, which sets the maintenance window.\"], \"diagnostics\": {\"systems\": {\"Brake System\": {\"score\": 75, \"condition\": \"Good\", \"recommendation\": \"Brake System: Schedule inspection within next 5,000 km. Current condition: Good.\"}, \"Tire System\": {\"score\": 75, \"condition\": \"Good\", \"recommendation\": \"Tire System: Schedule inspection within next 5,000 km. Current condition: Good.\"}, \"Battery System\": {\"score\": 50, \"condition\": \"N/A\", \"recommendation\": \"Battery System: Urgent inspection recommended. Condition reported as '' \\u2014 schedule within 1,000 km.\"}, \"Maintenance Record\": {\"score\": 50, \"condition\": \"N/A\", \"recommendation\": \"Maintenance Record: Urgent inspection recommended. Condition reported as '' \\u2014 schedule within 1,000 km.\"}, \"Mileage / Odometer\": {\"score\": 86.7, \"condition\": \"40,000 km\", \"recommendation\": \"Mileage / Odometer: No immediate action required. Continue regular service intervals.\"}}, \"most_vulnerable_component\": \"Battery System\", \"most_vulnerable_score\": 50, \"most_vulnerable_condition\": \"N/A\", \"most_vulnerable_recommendation\": \"Battery System: Urgent inspection recommended. Condition reported as '' \\u2014 schedule within 1,000 km.\", \"overall_risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"reported_issues\": 0, \"accident_history\": 0}, \"shap_explanation\": \"Maintenance was predicted mainly due to: **Mileage, Days Since Last Service**. Factors reducing maintenance risk: Brake Condition, Number Of Services.\", \"shap_top_factors\": [{\"feature\": \"Brake Condition\", \"impact\": -0.1894}, {\"feature\": \"Mileage\", \"impact\": 0.0884}, {\"feature\": \"Days Since Last Service\", \"impact\": 0.0517}], \"preliminary\": true, \"features_provided\": 7, \"features_total\": 10}\nCURRENT ML PREDICTION RESULT: {\"maintenance_risk\": \"HIGH\", \"model_confidence_percent\": 55.1, \"maintenance_recommended\": true, \"is_preliminary\": true, \"features_provided\": 7, \"features_total\": 10}\nSHAP EXPLANATION: 'Maintenance was predicted mainly due to: **Mileage, Days Since Last Service**. Factors reducing maintenance risk: Brake Condition, Number Of Services.'\nRECOMMENDATION TOOL OUTPUT: [\"Continue the regular service schedule and monitor for any new warning signs.\"]\nFEATURE COVERAGE: {\"known\": [\"accident_history\", \"avg_km_per_day\", \"brake_condition\", \"last_service_date\", \"mileage\", \"number_of_services\", \"odometer_reading\", \"tyre_condition\", \"vehicle_age\", \"vehicle_type\"], \"missing\": [], \"known_count\": 10, \"total\": 10, \"missing_labels\": {}}\nREQUIRED FOLLOW-UP QUESTION TO INCLUDE: 'Just to follow up on our last point, could you tell me if the car has ever been involved in any accidents?'\n\n\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\nGROUNDING & PHRASING RULES \u2014 FOLLOW EXACTL